responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "446277D64123CBEA63D52A91F11359E9", "Good work scouting the ruins.  However, while you were gone something unexpected happened.  A Sighted patrol made their way out of the city but when they returned one of the cultists were missing.   We recently stationed a 2nd Sword in the settlement to the southwest to keep an eye on the settlers.  I need you to head there to New Aela and warn Marshal McGannis about what\'s happening here.")
name: CSQ_DD_0010_SPH_ScoutOrithar_6_Response
